from solution import Solution

cases = [
    ([1,2,3,4,2,3,3,5,7], 2),

    ([6,7,8,9], 0),
    ([1], 0),

    ([1,2,3,1,2,3,4,5,6], 2),
    ([1,1,2,2,3,3], 2),

]

s = Solution()

    out = s.minimumOperations(nums)
    ok = out == expected
    print(i, nums, "=>", out, "(expected:", expected, ")", "OK" if ok else "FAIL")
    all_ok = all_ok and ok

print("ALL OK:" , all_ok)
